1/file transfer:
rsync -rPz [src_path] [remote_address]:[destin_path]

2/ssh:
ssh [remote_address]

3/sudo chmod a+rw /dev/ttyUSB0

4/apt update:
sudo apt-get install [software_name]

5/package_create:
catkin_make

6/joystick:
follow http://wiki.ros.org/joy/Tutorials/ConfiguringALinuxJoystick

launch joystick file: 
roslaunch turtlebot_teleop logitech.launch --screen
launch keyboard file:
roslaunch turtlebot_teleop keyboard_teleop.launch
